Text: InquiryPST Dear Real Estate Professional We make it simple to reach your Internet customers By taking advantage of this offer you can be a part of our very affordable International Agent Directory which is more easily accessed over the Internet because each city has its own dedicated web page which is registered with over search engines and directories You can have a word description of yourself with links to your Emails and personal web addresss for any city that you select for only per year we do not charge a monthly fee like most web sites and there are no hidden charges We also offer a multiple city discount which is six cities for a value To see a sample please visit usaazscohtm Scottsdale AZ For complete details on this offer and to request more information visit usamoreinfohtm To register online for this service visit usaonlineorderhtm All the services we offer the Real Estate Professional can be viewed at rpservhtm We hope to hear from you We will be happy to send you more information and answer your questions You are being contacted because one of our reviewers has recommended you for this offer If we reached you in error and want your name removed from our mailing list do not reply to sender You must use the removal form located at removalhtm Software Support Solutions wwwgreatrealtorscom E Baseline Rd PMB Mesa AZ Fax
